## Automate ALN Compliance Reporting in Batch Files

```batch
@echo off
REM ==== Automated ALN Compliance Reporter ====
REM Exports ALN usage logs for compliance review

setlocal EnableExtensions
set "ALNLOG=aln_usage.log"
set "REPORT=aln_compliance_report_%DATE%.txt"

echo === ALN Compliance Report %DATE% === > "%REPORT%"
type "%ALNLOG%" >> "%REPORT%"
echo REPORT GENERATED: "%REPORT%"
endlocal
exit /b 0
```
- Automate periodic exports to create documented ALN compliance history for audits.[7]

